's camera, photos, and microphone (like the ability to take photos, videos, view stored photos and videos, and access the microphone to record audio while recording video), and location information (precise location through methods like GPS signals)."},"collectsBiometricData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.8,"sourceQuote":"On iOS we use Apple''s TrueDepth camera to improve the quality of Lenses. Note, however, that this information is used in real time — we don''t store this information on our servers or share it with third parties."},"collectsHealthData":{"value":false,"confidence":0.7,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not explicitly mention health or medical data collection."},"collectsFinancialData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"payment and related information (like your physical address, so we can ship the product to you, payment information, so we can process the payment, and transaction history)"}},"dataSharing":{"soldToThirdParties":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy mentions sharing with service providers, business partners, and others but does not explicitly state whether data is sold. Defaulting to consumer-unfavorable interpretation."},"sharedForAdvertising":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"We share your information, such as device and usage information, with industry partners working to prevent fraud. We share your information with business and integrated partners in order to provide the Services... data from advertisers (information from advertisers, app developers, publishers, and other third parties to help target or measure the performance of ads)"},"crossSiteTracking":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"we may use information collected on an advertiser''s website to show you more relevant ads. Most web browsers are set to accept cookies by default... we may use these technologies to collect information when you interact with Services we offer through one of our partners."},"usedForProfiling":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"infer your interests based on your content or activity, or customize the content we show you, including ads. For example, if you watch barista content on Spotlight, talk to My AI about your favorite espresso machine, or save a lot of coffee-related Snaps in your Memories, we may highlight coffee shops on the Snap Map when you visit a new city or show you content about coffee that you may find interesting or relevant."},"usedToTrainAI":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"our algorithms and machine learning models take into account the conversations Snapchatters are having with My AI to improve the responses from My AI... We use algorithms and machine learning models for personalization, advertising, safety and security, fairness and inclusivity, augmented reality, and to prevent abuse or other Terms of Service violations."},"thirdPartyCount":null},"retention":{"retentionDays":null,"indefinite":true,"sourceQuote":"As a general rule, we keep information as long as you tell us to, and otherwise as long as we need it to provide our Services, or as required by law... we store your basic account details — like your name, phone number, and email address — to maintain your account."},"consumerRights":{"rightToAccess":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Access and update your information. You can access and edit most of your basic account information right in our Services."},"rightToDelete":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Delete your information. If you want to delete your account, learn how here. You can also delete some information within our Services, like content you''ve saved to Memories, content you''ve shared with My AI, Spotlight submissions, and more."},"rightToPortability":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Download your data. You can make a request in our Download My Data tool to export a copy of your Snapchat information."},"rightToCorrect":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"Access and update your information. You can access and edit most of your basic account information right in our Services."},"rightToOptOut":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"Set advertising preferences. We try to show you ads that we think will be relevant to your interests, but if you''d like to have a less personalized experience, you can change your advertising settings in the Snapchat app."},"rightToNonDiscrimination":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not explicitly mention right to non-discrimination. Defaulting to false with low confidence."}},"signalHonoring":{"honorsGPC":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Global Privacy Control (GPC). Defaulting to not honored."},"honorsDNT":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Do Not Track (DNT). Defaulting to not honored."}},"security":{"measures":[{"name":"two-factor authentication","sourceQuote":"we provide two-factor authentication to help protect your account and can send you email or text messages if we notice any suspicious activity"},{"name":"URL scanning","sourceQuote":"We also scan URLs sent on Snapchat to see if that webpage is potentially harmful, and can give you a warning about it."},{"name":"fraud detection","sourceQuote":"We share your information, such as device and usage information, with industry partners working to prevent fraud."}]}}', 44, 'D', 'Poor', '#c2410c', '1', '[{"key":"soldToThirdParties","label":"Data sold to third parties","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"sharedForAdvertising","label":"Data shared for advertising","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"crossSiteTracking","label":"Cross-site tracking","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"usedForProfiling","label":"Used for profiling / AI decisions","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"usedToTrainAI","label":"Used to train AI models","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsPreciseGeolocation","label":"Collects preci