, time, and referrer URL of your request."},{"name":"Search terms","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"Terms you search for"},{"name":"Videos watched","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"Videos you watch"},{"name":"Voice and audio information","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"Voice and audio information"},{"name":"Purchase activity","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"Purchase activity"},{"name":"Communication contacts","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"People with whom you communicate or share content"},{"name":"Call and message logs","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"If you use our services to make and receive calls or send and receive messages, we may collect call and message log information like your phone number, calling-party number, receiving-party number"},{"name":"Location data","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"We collect location information when you use our services"},{"name":"Biometric information","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Biometric information if you choose to provide it, such as fingerprints in Google''s product development studies."},{"name":"Health information","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Health information if you choose to provide it, such as your medical history, vital signs and health metrics (like blood glucose levels)"}],"collectsPreciseGeolocation":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Depending on these settings, this may include precise location data, for example GPS data for Android features like navigation or finding your phone."},"collectsBiometricData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"Biometric information if you choose to provide it, such as fingerprints in Google''s product development studies."},"collectsHealthData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Health information if you choose to provide it, such as your medical history, vital signs and health metrics (like blood glucose levels)"},"collectsFinancialData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"You can also choose to add a phone number or payment information to your account."}},"dataSharing":{"soldToThirdParties":{"value":false,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Google does not sell your personal information. Google also does not \"share\" your personal information as that term is defined in the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)."},"sharedForAdvertising":{"value":true,"confidence":0.92,"sourceQuote":"We may also show you personalized ads based on your interests and activity across Google services. For example, if you search for \"mountain bikes,\" you may see ads for sports equipment on YouTube."},"crossSiteTracking":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"This activity might come from your use of Google services, like from syncing your account with Chrome or your visits to sites and apps that partner with Google."},"usedForProfiling":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"We use the information we collect to customize our services for you, including providing recommendations, personalized content, and customized search results."},"usedToTrainAI":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"For example, we use publicly available information to help train Google''s AI models and build products and features like Google Translate, Gemini Apps, and Cloud AI capabilities."},"thirdPartyCount":null},"retention":{"retentionDays":null,"indefinite":true,"sourceQuote":"We retain the data we collect for different periods of time depending on what it is, how we use it, and how you configure your settings. We keep some data until you delete your Google Account, such as information about how often you use our services. And some data we retain for longer periods of time when necessary for legitimate business or legal purposes."},"consumerRights":{"rightToAccess":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"U.S. state privacy laws also provide the right to request information about how Google collects, uses, and discloses your information. And they give you the right to access your information, sometimes in a portable format"},"rightToDelete":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"To delete your information, you can: Delete your content from specific Google services, Search for and then delete specific items from your account using My Activity, Delete specific Google products, including your information associated with those products, Delete your entire Google Account"},"rightToPortability":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"You can export a copy of content in your Google Account if you want to back it up or use it with a service outside of Google."},"rightToCorrect":{"value":true,"confidence":0.85,"sourceQuote":"When you''re signed in, you can always review and update information by visiting the services you use."},"rightToOptOut":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"Many of these laws also provide the right to opt out of certain forms of profiling and targeted advertising."},"rightToNonDiscrimination":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"They also provide the right to not be discriminated against for exercising these privacy rights."}},"signalHonoring":{"honorsGPC":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Global Privacy Control (GPC). Defaulting to not honored."},"honorsDNT":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Do Not Track (DNT). Defaulting to not honored."}},"security":{"measures":[{"name":"Encryption in transit","sourceQuote":"We use encryption to keep your data private while in transit"},{"name":"Safe Browsing","sourceQuote":"We offer a range of security features, like Safe Browsing, Security Checkup, and 2 Step Verification to help you protect your account"},{"name":"2-Step Verification","sourceQuote":"We offer a range of security features, like Safe Browsing, Security Checkup, and 2 Step Verification to help you protect your account"},{"name":"Access controls","sourceQuote":"We restrict access to personal information to Google employees, contractors, a