e some of the data you provided us directly within the service. You can also close your account as explained here and we''ll delete your data as laid out in this Privacy Policy."},"rightToPortability":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"You can also retrieve a copy of your data by following the process explained here."},"rightToCorrect":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"You can update your data directly within the service by simply updating your profile. If you wish to rectify other data, please contact us here."},"rightToOptOut":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"If you live in the United States, you may opt out of activities that may fall under the legal definitions of ''targeted advertising,'' ''sales,'' or ''sharing'' under applicable laws. To opt out, please visit the ''Your Privacy Choices'' link in the footer of our website and in the Settings menu of the app."},"rightToNonDiscrimination":{"value":false,"confidence":0.6,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not explicitly mention right to non-discrimination for exercising privacy rights."}},"signalHonoring":{"honorsGPC":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Global Privacy Control (GPC). Defaulting to not honored."},"honorsDNT":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Do Not Track (DNT). Defaulting to not honored."}},"security":{"measures":[{"name":"Safety retention window","sourceQuote":"To protect the safety and security of our members, we implement a safety retention window of three months following account closure or up to two years following an account ban."},{"name":"Identity verification","sourceQuote":"For your protection and the protection of all of our members, we may ask you for information to verify your identity or authority to act on behalf of a member before we can answer the above requests."},{"name":"Cross-platform safety measures","sourceQuote":"Match Group considers the safety and security of members a top priority. If you were banned from another Match Group service, your data can be shared with us to allow us to take necessary actions, including closing your account or preventing you from creating an account on our service."}]}}', 24, 'F', 'Failing', '#b91c1c', '1', '[{"key":"soldToThirdParties","label":"Data sold to third parties","points":-25,"triggered":true},{"key":"sharedForAdvertising","label":"Data shared for advertising","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"crossSiteTracking","label":"Cross-site tracking","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"usedForProfiling","label":"Used for profiling / AI decisions","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"usedToTrainAI","label":"Used to train AI models","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsPreciseGeolocation","label":"Collects precise geolocation","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsBiometricData","label":"Collects biometric data","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsHealthData","label":"Collects health data","points":-5,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsFinancialData","label":"Collects financial data","points":-3,"triggered":true},{"key":"doesNotHonorGPC","label":"Does not honor GPC","points":-5,"triggered":true},{"key":"doesNotHonorDNT","label":"Does not honor DNT","points":-2,"triggered":true},{"key":"thirdPartiesOver10","label":"More than 10 third parties","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"thirdParties6To10","label":"6–10 third parties","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"retentionIndefinite","label":"Retention is indefinite","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"retentionOver3Years","label":"Retention longer than 3 years","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"retentionOver1Year","label":"Retention longer than 1 year","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"consumerRights","label":"Consumer rights available","points":10,"triggered":true,"detail":"5 of 6 rights offered"},{"key":"securityMeasures","label":"Security measures in place","points":6,"triggered":true,"detail":"3 of 5 measure