 your co-travelers'' passport or national ID information"},{"name":"national ID information","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"we may be required to collect additional information from you including your and your co-travelers'' passport or national ID information"},{"name":"IP address","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"we automatically collect certain information. This includes your IP address"},{"name":"device information","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"some information about your device''s hardware and software (such as the type of operating system, internet browser and mobile app version you use)"},{"name":"browsing behavior","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"We also collect information about clicks you make and which pages are shown to you from our platform"},{"name":"health data","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Health data: current or former physical or mental medical conditions, health status, injury or disability information, medical procedures performed"},{"name":"biometric data","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Other special categories of personal data: racial or ethnic origin, biometric data (for example from a passport or identity document that is used to identify the passport or document holder)"},{"name":"financial data","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Financial information: payment card number and information, bank account numbers and account details, income, and other financial information"}],"collectsPreciseGeolocation":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"you can decide to allow Booking.com to use your current location or grant us access to other details. This helps us give you the best possible service and experience by, for example, suggesting the nearest restaurants or attractions to your location"},"collectsBiometricData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"If you want a verified account badge in those jurisdictions where it is available, we may ask for a copy of your identification (a passport or ID card) and a ''selfie'' to help us confirm it is you"},"collectsHealthData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Health data: current or former physical or mental medical conditions, health status, injury or disability information, medical procedures performed, relevant personal habits (e.g. smoking or consumption of alcohol), prescription information, medical history"},"collectsFinancialData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Financial information: payment card number and information, bank account numbers and account details, income, and other financial information"}},"dataSharing":{"soldToThirdParties":{"value":true,"confidence":0.85,"sourceQuote":"We may share certain elements of your personal data with third parties, which under US state privacy laws may be considered the sale of personal data. This may include information related to inferences and analytics."},"sharedForAdvertising":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"We may share some of your personal data (such as identifiers) with advertising partners, as part of the marketing of our trip services via third parties (to ensure that relevant advertisements are shown to the right audience)"},"crossSiteTracking":{"value":true,"confidence":0.88,"sourceQuote":"Marketing cookies: We and our partners use marketing cookies, including social media cookies, to collect information about your browsing behavior that helps us and our partners decide which products to show you on and off our site"},"usedForProfiling":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"We use AI to predict the optimal/most relevant category of products for you and bring the best options to your attention. This may include sending you details of a trip we think you would be interested in, displaying tailored complementary trip offerings on our website, and ranking search results to put the best matches at the top of your feed"},"usedToTrainAI":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Personal data may be used to develop, train, and fine-tune AI systems such as generative AI models. These models enable you to use natural language to ask questions about a trip or service and to receive AI-generated relevant responses or itinerary suggestions."},"thirdPartyCount":null},"retention":{"retentionDays":null,"indefinite":false,"sourceQuote":"Generally, we keep your personal data for as long as is necessary to: Enable you to use our services or to provide our services to you, Prevent and detect online fraud attempts and/or other illegal activities, Comply with legal obligations such as those from accounting and tax laws, Resolve any disputes and legal claims"},"consumerRights":{"rightToAccess":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Access: You can ask us for a copy of the personal data we hold about you."},"rightToDelete":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Erasure: You can ask us to erase the personal data we hold about you when, for example, it is no longer needed or we have asked for your consent and you later withdraw it."},"rightToPortability":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Portability: In certain situations, you can also ask us to provide you with specific personal data you have given us for possible transmission to a third party."},"rightToCorrect":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Correction: You can inform us anytime of changes to your personal data and ask us to correct certain personal data we hold about you."},"rightToOptOut":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"Opt out of the selling of data: You can ask us not to sell your personal data to third parties. Opt out of targeted advertising: You can ask us not to use your personal data for targeted advertising."},"rightToNonDiscrimination":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not explicitly mention right to non-discrimination. Defaulting to not provided."}},"signalHonoring":{"honorsGPC":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Global Privacy Control (GPC). Defaulting to not honored."},"honorsDNT":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Do Not Track (DNT). Defaulting to not honored."}},"security":{"measures":[{"name":"Comprehensive security framework","sourceQuote":"Maintain a comprehensive framework of security policies, procedures, and protocols"},{"name":"Cybersecurity personnel","sourceQuote":"Employ personnel dedicated to cybersecurity and data protection"},{"name":"Security training","sourceQuote":"Keep staff alert to security risks through continual security training and awareness activities"},{"name":"Encryption","sourceQuote":"Use up-to-date security technologies such as encryption and data leakage prevention"},{"name":"Access controls","sourceQuote":"Use identity and access management and other logical and physical access restrictions to control that only authorized personnel can access personal data"},{"name":"Incident response protocols","sourceQuote":"Maintain and test protocols to respond to reports about possible incidents and data breaches"}]}}', 28, 'F', 'Failing', '#b91c1c', '1', '[{"key":"soldToThirdParties","label":"Data sold to third parties","points":-25,"triggered":true},{"key":"sharedForAdvertising","label":"Data shared for advertising","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"crossSiteTracking","label":"Cross-site tracking","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"usedForProfiling","label":"Used for profiling / AI decisions","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"usedToTrainAI","label":"Used to train AI models","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsPreciseGeolocation","label":"Collects precise geolocation","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsBiometricData","label":"Collects biometric data","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsHealthData","label":"Collects health data","points":-5,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsFinancialData","label":"Collects financial data","points":-3,"triggered":true},{"key":"doesNotHonorGPC","label":"Does not honor GPC","points":-5,"triggered":true},{"key":"doesNotHonorDNT","label":"Does not honor DNT","points":-2,"triggered":true},{"key":"thirdPartiesOver10","label":"More than 10 third parties","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"thirdParties6To10","label":"6–10 third parties","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"retentionIndefinite","label":"Retention is indefinite","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"retentionOver3Years","label":"Retention longer than 3 years","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"retentionOver1Year","label":"Retention longer than 1 year","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"consumerRights","label":"Consumer rights available","points":10,"triggered":true,"detail":"5 of 6 rights offered"},{"key":"securityMeasures","label":"Security measures in place","points":10,"triggered":true,"detail":"5 of 5 measures"}]', 'claude-sonnet-4-20250514', 22391, 2615, 111684, 0, '2026-03-21T06:51:41Z');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO extractions (id, policy_id, company_id, facts_json, score, letter, grade_label, grade_color, rubric_version, breakdown_json, model, input_tokens, output_tokens, latency_ms, chunked, created_at) VALUES (42, 42, 42, '{"metadata":{"schemaVersion":"1.0.0","companyName":"Microsoft Copilot / Office (Microsoft Corporation)","policyUrl":"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/privacy/privacystatement","analyzedAt":"2026-03-21T06:54:08.301Z","policyHash":"9559bd9c597b1e84839ebee0e6d030bc36cc9a75c8197bc2ab9dc6731a3b3c08","policyEffectiveDate":"March 2026"},"dataCollection":{"items":[{"name":"Name and contact data","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"Your first and last name, email address, postal address, phone number, and other similar contact data."},{"name":"Credentials","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Passwords, password hints, and similar security information used for authentication and account access."},{"name":"Payment data","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Data to process payments, such as your payment instrument number (such as a credit card number) and the security code associated with your payment instrument."},{"name":"Location data","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Data about your device''s location, which can be either precise or imprecise. For example, we collect location data using Global Navigation Satellite System (GNSS) (e.g., GPS) and data about nearby cell towers and Wi-Fi hotspots."},{"name":"Biometric data and identifiers","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Data about you resulting from specific technical processing relating to your physical, physiological, or behavioral characteristics which allow or confirm unique identification."},{"name":"Voice data","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Your voice data, sometimes referred to as ''voice clips'', such as search queries, commands, or dictation you speak, which may include background sounds."},{"name":"Content","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Content of your files and communications you input, upload, receive, create, and control. For example, if you transmit a file using Teams to another Teams user, we need to collect the content of that file to display it to you and the other user."},{"name":"Health data","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"In the United States, we provide personalized advertising based on a limited number of standard, non-sensitive health-related interest categories, including allergies, arthritis, cholesterol, cold and flu, diabetes, gastrointestinal health, headache / migraine, healthy eating, healthy heart, men''s health, oral health, osteoporosis, skin health, sleep, and vision / eye care."},{"name":"Demographic data","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"Data about you such as your age, gender, country, and preferred language."},{"name":"Device and usage data","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"Data about your device and the product and features you use, including information about your hardware and software, how our products perform, as well as your settings."},{"name":"Voice recordings","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Microsoft collects and uses your voice recordings to provide the speech recognition service"},{"name":"Biometric data (iris, face recognition)","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"cameras can be used to sign you in automatically using your iris. To do this, HoloLens takes an image of your iris"},{"name":"Text and handwriting samples","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"You also can choose to help Microsoft improve inking and typing recognition by sending inking and typing diagnostic data"},{"name":"Browsing history and search queries","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"Browser activity, including browsing history and search terms, in Microsoft browsers"},{"name":"Documents and file content","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Copilot will use the content in your files only when you ask it to perform a specific action on that specific content"},{"name":"Contacts and communication data","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Teams will sync your device and Outlook contacts periodically"},{"name":"Photos and videos","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Phone Link allows you to copy, share, edit, save, or delete photos from your Android phone"},{"name":"Text messages and call history","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Phone Link allows you to view text messages delivered to your Android phone on your Windows device"},{"name":"Biometric data (face, fingerprint, iris)","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Windows Hello uses your face, fingerprint, or iris to identify you based on a set of unique points or features that are extracted from the image and stored on your device as a template"},{"name":"Device information","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"standard device data, such as your device IP address, device software version, your regional and language settings"},{"name":"Audio recordings","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Sound Recorder app is a versatile tool designed for capturing audio via your microphone"},{"name":"Gaming data","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"Which games you play and apps you use, your game progress, achievements, play time per game, and other play statistics"},{"name":"Social interactions","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"Social activity, including chat data and interactions with other gamers, and connections you make"}],"collectsPreciseGeolocation":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Microsoft operates a location service that helps determine the precise geographic location of a specific Windows device. Depending on the capabilities of the device, the device''s location can be determined with varying degrees of accuracy and may in some cases be determined precisely."},"collectsBiometricData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Windows Hello uses your face, fingerprint, or iris to identify you based on a set of unique points or features that are extracted from the image and stored on your device as a template"},"collectsHealthData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.8,"sourceQuote":"In the United States, we provide personalized advertising based on a limited number of standard, non-sensitive health-related interest categories, including allergies, arthritis, cholesterol, cold and flu, diabetes, gastrointestinal health, headache / migraine, healthy eating, healthy heart, men''s health, oral health, osteoporosis, skin health, sleep, and vision / eye care."},"collectsFinancialData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.6,"sourceQuote":"MSN Money allow you to access personal finance information from third-party financial institutions. MSN Money only displays this information and does not store it on our servers"}},"dataSharing":{"soldToThirdParties":{"value":false,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"We do not sell your personal data. So, we do not offer an opt-out to the sale of personal data."},"sharedForAdvertising":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"We also use the data we collect to provide you with advertisements that may be of interest to you"},"crossSiteTracking":{"value":true,"confidence":0.7,"sourceQuote":"Microsoft Store uses your device identifier to manage product rights tied to a specific device"},"usedForProfiling":{"value":true,"confidence":0.85,"sourceQuote":"We use your location to provide you with relevant content such as local weather and news"},"usedToTrainAI":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"Xbox offers optional AI-enhanced features, including our Support Virtual Agents and Copilot in Xbox, that allow you to enter a prompt via text or voice. To provide a response, these AI-enhanced features use your prompt"},"thirdPartyCount":0},"retention":{"retentionDays":null,"indefinite":true,"sourceQuote":"Microsoft retains personal data for as long as necessary to provide the products and fulfill the transactions you have requested, or for other legitimate purposes such as complying with our legal obligations, resolving disputes, and enforcing our agreements. Because these needs can vary for different data types, the context of our interactions with you or your use of products, actual retention periods can vary significantly."},"consumerRights":{"rightToAccess":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"You can request access to, erasure of, and updates to your personal data."},"rightToDelete":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"You can request access to, erasure of, and updates to your personal data."},"rightToPortability":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not explicitly mention data portability rights, defaulting to unfavorable interpretation"},"rightToCorrect":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not explicitly mention right to correct personal data"},"rightToOptOut":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"You may indicate your choice to opt-out of the sharing of your personal data with third parties for personalized advertising on third party sites by visiting our sharing opt-out page."},"rightToNonDiscrimination":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention right to non-discrimination"}},"signalHonoring":{"honorsGPC":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Global Privacy Control (GPC). Defaulting to not honored"},"honorsDNT":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Do Not Track (DNT). Defaulting to not honored"}},"security":{"measures":[{"name":"Encryption","sourceQuote":"When we transmit highly confidential data (such as a credit card number or password) over the internet, we protect it through the use of encryption."},{"name":"Limited access systems","sourceQuote":"we store the personal data you provide on computer systems that have limited access and are in controlled facilities."},{"name":"Compliance with data protection laws","sourceQuote":"Microsoft complies with applicable data protection laws, including applicable security breach notification laws."},{"name":"Device encryption","sourceQuote":"Device encryption helps protect the data stored on your device by encrypting it using BitLocker Drive Encryption technology"},{"name":"Windows Hello biometric security","sourceQuote":"All data is stored locally on the device and is protected with Windows Hello Enhanced Sign-in Security (ESS), which provides more secure biometric sign-ins"},{"name":"Microsoft Defender SmartScreen","sourceQuote":"Microsoft Defender SmartScreen helps protect you when using our services by identifying threats to you, your device, and your passwords"},{"name":"Microsoft Defender Antivirus","sourceQuote":"Microsoft Defender Antivirus looks for malware and other unwanted software, potentially unwanted apps, and other malicious content on your device"},{"name":"Device-based biometric storage","sourceQuote":"Biometric verification data that''s used when you sign in doesn''t leave your device"},{"name":"Encryption of financial credentials","sourceQuote":"Your sign-in credentials used to access your financial information from third parties are encrypted on your device and are not sent to Microsoft"},{"name":"Anti-cheat and fraud prevention","sourceQuote":"In order to detect and prevent fraud and cheating, we may use anti-cheat and fraud prevention tools, applications, and other technologies"}]}}', 39, 'F', 'Failing', '#b91c1c', '1', '[{"key":"soldToThirdParties","label":"Data sold to third parties","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"sharedForAdvertising","label":"Data shared for advertising","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"crossSiteTracking","label":"Cross-site tracking","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"usedForProfiling","label":"Used for profiling / AI decisions","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"usedToTrainAI","label":"Used to train AI models","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsPreciseGeolocation","label":"Collects precise geolocation","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsBiometricData","label":"Collects biometric data","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsHealthData","label":"Collects health data","points":-5,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsFinancialData","label":"Collects financial data","points":-3,"triggered":true},{"key":"doesNotHonorGPC","label":"Does not honor GPC","points":-5,"triggered":true},{"key":"doesNotHonorDNT","label":"Does not honor DNT","points":-2,"triggered":true},{"key":"thirdPartiesOver10","label":"More than 10 third parties","points":0,"triggered":false,"detail":"0 third parties disclosed"},{"key":"thirdParties6To10","label":"6–10 third parties","points":0,"triggered":false,"detail":"0 third parties disclosed"},{"key":"retentionIndefinite","label":"Retention is indefinite","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"retentionOver3Years","label":"Retention longer than 3 years","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"retentionOver1Year","label":"Retention longer than 1 year","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"consumerRights","label":"Consumer rights available","points":6,"triggered":true,"detail":"3 of 6 rights offered"},{"key":"securityMeasures","label":"Security measures in place","points":10,"triggered":true,"detail":"5 of 5 measures"}]', 'claude-sonnet-4-20250514', 72600, 6090, 258567, 1, '2026-03-21T06:54:08Z');
