ristics, including your facial geometry and/or voiceprint"},{"name":"Facial Geometry","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"Zoom may process data about your unique physical characteristics, including your facial geometry and/or voiceprint"}],"collectsPreciseGeolocation":{"value":false,"confidence":0.8,"sourceQuote":"IP address (which may be used to infer general location at a city or country level)"},"collectsBiometricData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Zoom may process data about your unique physical characteristics, including your facial geometry and/or voiceprint, for the purpose of offering the features"},"collectsHealthData":{"value":false,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention health or medical data collection"},"collectsFinancialData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"billing and transaction information"}},"dataSharing":{"soldToThirdParties":{"value":false,"confidence":0.6,"sourceQuote":"We do not sell your personal data in the conventional sense. However, like many companies, we may use advertising and analytics services"},"sharedForAdvertising":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"we may use advertising and analytics services that are intended to analyze your interactions with our website or app, based on information obtained from cookies or other trackers, including for delivering advertising to you (such as interest-based, targeted, or cross-context behavioral advertising)"},"crossSiteTracking":{"value":true,"confidence":0.85,"sourceQuote":"These third-party partners may receive information about your activities on Zoom''s website through third-party cookies placed on Zoom''s website"},"usedForProfiling":{"value":true,"confidence":0.8,"sourceQuote":"to provide, support, and improve Zoom products and services and technical infrastructure, and for business services such as payment processing"},"usedToTrainAI":{"value":false,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Zoom does not use any of your audio, video, chat, screen sharing, attachments or other communications-like Customer Content (such as poll results, whiteboard and reactions) to train Zoom''s or its third-party artificial intelligence models"},"thirdPartyCount":null},"retention":{"retentionDays":null,"indefinite":true,"sourceQuote":"We retain personal data for as long as required to engage in the uses described in this Privacy Statement, unless a longer retention period is required by applicable law"},"consumerRights":{"rightToAccess":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Access the categories and specific pieces of personal data Zoom has collected"},"rightToDelete":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Delete personal data under certain circumstances"},"rightToPortability":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"obtain the personal data in a portable and, to the extent technically feasible, readily usable format"},"rightToCorrect":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Correct personal data under certain circumstances"},"rightToOptOut":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Opt out of the ''sale'' of personal data or ''sharing'' of personal data for targeted advertising purposes"},"rightToNonDiscrimination":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Zoom will not discriminate against you for exercising any of these rights"}},"signalHonoring":{"honorsGPC":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"Residents of California, Colorado, Connecticut, Montana, Nebraska, New Hampshire, and Texas may also set the Global Privacy Control (GPC) to opt out of the ''sale'' or ''sharing'' of your personal information for targeted advertising"},"honorsDNT":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Do Not Track (DNT) signals. Defaulting to not honored."}},"security":{"measures":[{"name":"Authentication and fraud detection","sourceQuote":"To authenticate accounts and activity, detect, investigate, and prevent malicious conduct, fraudulent activity or unsafe expe