n you install, access, or use our Services."},{"name":"Precise location information","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"We collect and use precise location information from your device with your permission when you choose to use location-related features"},{"name":"IP address","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"This includes information such as hardware model, operating system information, battery level, signal strength, app version, browser information, mobile network, connection information (including phone number, mobile operator or ISP), language and time zone, IP address"}],"collectsPreciseGeolocation":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"We collect and use precise location information from your device with your permission when you choose to use location-related features"},"collectsBiometricData":{"value":false,"confidence":0.8,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention collection of biometric data such as fingerprints, face recognition, or voiceprints."},"collectsHealthData":{"value":false,"confidence":0.8,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention collection of health, medical, fitness, or wellness data."},"collectsFinancialData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"If you use our payments services, or use our Services meant for purchases or other financial transactions, we process additional information about you, including payment account and transaction information."}},"dataSharing":{"soldToThirdParties":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy mentions sharing with third-party service providers and Meta Companies but does not explicitly state whether data is sold. Defaulting to consumer-unfavorable interpretation due to ambiguity."},"sharedForAdvertising":{"value":true,"confidence":0.85,"sourceQuote":"improving their services and your experiences using them, such as making suggestions for you (for example, of friends or group connections, or of interesting content), personalizing features and content, helping you complete purchases and