ird party companies"},"crossSiteTracking":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"These cookies and other technologies may be used to track you over time and across devices"},"usedForProfiling":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"Inferences drawn from any of the information we collect to create a profile about you reflecting information such as your preferences and characteristics"},"usedToTrainAI":{"value":false,"confidence":0.6,"sourceQuote":"Policy mentions using data to ''improve our business'' and ''internal research for technological development'' but does not explicitly mention AI training"},"thirdPartyCount":null},"retention":{"retentionDays":null,"indefinite":true,"sourceQuote":"Your Personal Information will be retained as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes we have outlined in Section 4 of this Notice, unless we are required to do so by applicable law... Once you / your company has terminated the contractual relationship with us or otherwise ended your relationship with us, we may retain your Personal Information in our systems and records"},"consumerRights":{"rightToAccess":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"You have the right to (1) request to know more about and access your Personal Information, including in a portable format"},"rightToDelete":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"You have the right to... (2) request deletion of your Personal Information"},"rightToPortability":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"You have the right to (1) request to know more about and access your Personal Information, including in a portable format"},"rightToCorrect":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"You have the right to... (3) request correction of inaccurate Personal Information"},"rightToOptOut":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"You can opt out of cookie-based ad targeting on our website by following the prompts and making a Privacy Request"},"rightToNonDiscrimination":{"value":true,"con