 voice channel, snippets of voice chat are stored on your device"},{"name":"face images","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"When you use MetaHuman to create in-game characters, we collect images of your face to generate a face mesh"},{"name":"IP address","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"technical information about the computer, device, hardware, or software you use to access the Epic Services, including IP address, device ID"},{"name":"device ID","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"technical information about the computer, device, hardware, or software you use to access the Epic Services, including IP address, device ID"},{"name":"location information","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"general location information about your device, typically inferred from its IP address"},{"name":"usage information","sensitive":false,"sourceQuote":"usage information and statistics about how you interact with the Epic Services, including the application or game used, duration and timing of use, gameplay attempts, progression and results"},{"name":"government ID","sensitive":true,"sourceQuote":"in some cases, sensitive personal information (e.g., account log-in credentials and, if you list, sell, or trade creative content in one of our marketplaces, government ID)"}],"collectsPreciseGeolocation":{"value":false,"confidence":0.8,"sourceQuote":"general location information about your device, typically inferred from its IP address"},"collectsBiometricData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"When you use MetaHuman to create in-game characters, we collect images of your face to generate a face mesh"},"collectsHealthData":{"value":false,"confidence":0.85,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention health, medical, fitness, or wellness data collection"},"collectsFinancialData":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"When you make a purchase on the Epic Games Store, depending on which payment method you use, we may collect your payment information (e.g., credit card number and expiration date, name, and region information)"}},"dataSharing":{"soldToThirdParties":{"value":false,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"Epic does not sell or share the personal information it collects"},"sharedForAdvertising":{"value":true,"confidence":0.75,"sourceQuote":"marketing and advertising partners"},"crossSiteTracking":{"value":true,"confidence":0.7,"sourceQuote":"When you interact with an ad for the Epic Services on a third-party website or service, we may receive related information from the company operating that website or service"},"usedForProfiling":{"value":true,"confidence":0.8,"sourceQuote":"To personalize the Epic Services (legitimate interests): For example, we may use your information to present content, features, and recommendations tailored to you, or inferred from your activity, including by suggesting games in genres you frequently purchase"},"usedToTrainAI":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"To understand and improve the Epic Services (legitimate interests): For example, we may use your information to analyze your use of the Epic Services, support auditing, and improve features, technologies, and processes, including by training machine learning technologies to detect and moderate illegal, harmful, toxic, and fraudulent conduct and content"},"thirdPartyCount":8},"retention":{"retentionDays":null,"indefinite":true,"sourceQuote":"We generally retain information for as long as we reasonably need it for the purposes described in Section 4 (Why Do We Process Information?), unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law. For example, if you create an Epic account, we will generally retain the information associated with your account (e.g., name, public-facing display name, password, country, and email address) for as long as needed to maintain your account"},"consumerRights":{"rightToAccess":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"You can request that we provide access to, or correct or delete, information we have collected from you"},"rightToDelete":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"You can request that we provide access to, or correct or delete, information we have collected from you"},"rightToPortability":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"data portability, including receiving a copy of your personal data"},"rightToCorrect":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"You can correct your information through your Epic account"},"rightToOptOut":{"value":true,"confidence":0.9,"sourceQuote":"You can change your email marketing preferences at any time (e.g., by using the opt-out mechanism in our marketing emails, updating your Epic account settings, or contacting us directly)"},"rightToNonDiscrimination":{"value":true,"confidence":0.95,"sourceQuote":"We will not discriminate against you for exercising any of your privacy rights under applicable law"}},"signalHonoring":{"honorsGPC":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Global Privacy Control (GPC). Defaulting to not honored."},"honorsDNT":{"value":false,"confidence":0.4,"sourceQuote":"Policy does not mention Do Not Track (DNT). Defaulting to not honored."}},"security":{"measures":[{"name":"administrative safeguards","sourceQuote":"We maintain appropriate administrative, technical, contractual, and physical safeguards to secure your information from accidental, unlawful, or unauthorized destruction, loss, alteration, access, disclosure, use, or other unlawful forms of processing"},{"name":"technical safeguards","sourceQuote":"We maintain appropriate administrative, technical, contractual, and physical safeguards to secure your information from accidental, unlawful, or unauthorized destruction, loss, alteration, access, disclosure, use, or other unlawful forms of processing"},{"name":"physical safeguards","sourceQuote":"We maintain appropriate administrative, technical, contractual, and physical safeguards to secure your information from accidental, unlawful, or unauthorized destruction, loss, alteration, access, disclosure, use, or other unlawful forms of processing"},{"name":"contractual safeguards","sourceQuote":"We maintain appropriate administrative, technical, contractual, and physical safeguards to secure your information from accidental, unlawful, or unauthorized destruction, loss, alteration, access, disclosure, use, or other unlawful forms of processing"},{"name":"breach notification","sourceQuote":"If we become aware of unauthorized disclosure of your information, we will notify you as required by law and take appropriate steps to help secure your information"}]}}', 53, 'D', 'Poor', '#c2410c', '1', '[{"key":"soldToThirdParties","label":"Data sold to third parties","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"sharedForAdvertising","label":"Data shared for advertising","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"crossSiteTracking","label":"Cross-site tracking","points":-10,"triggered":true},{"key":"usedForProfiling","label":"Used for profiling / AI decisions","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"usedToTrainAI","label":"Used to train AI models","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsPreciseGeolocation","label":"Collects precise geolocation","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"collectsBiometricData","label":"Collects biometric data","points":-8,"triggered":true},{"key":"collectsHealthData","label":"Collects health data","points":0,"triggered":false},{"key":"collectsFinancialData","label":"Collects financial data","points":-3,"triggered":true},{"key":"doesNotHonorGPC","label":"Does not honor GPC","points":-5,"triggered":true},{"key":"doesNotHonorDNT","label":"Does not honor DNT","points":-2,"triggered":true},{"key":"thirdPartiesOver10","label":"More than 10 third parties","points":0,"triggered":false,"detail":"8 third parties disclosed"},{"key":"thirdParties6To10","label":"6–10 third parties","points":-5,"triggered":true,"detail":"8 third parties disclosed"},{"key":"retentionIndefinite","label":"Retention is indefinite","points":-10,"t